Description: Imari Partners specializes in an entrepreneurial US-Japan business development and turnarounds.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Imari Partners specializes in an entrepreneurial US-Japan business development and turnarounds.  For many US companies, cash preservation and Japanese market entry effort require a fine balancing act. The traditional "find a distributor" approach is no longer a valid market entry model, as today's technology becoming more complex and early adapter customers demanding direct vendor leadership and support from start.  Alternatively, hiring one or two local personnel seems to be a better choice, however, being shy of a critical mass formation has its demerits and stress on both the local staff and the customers. Therefore the intended growth strategy is somewhat stimied and the investment not optimized.   Imari Partners offers a hands on representation of an US corporation in the Japanese market, initially staffing the core team with its trans-cultural operational and executive staff members.  As strategic growth plans are formulated, appropriate business structure is implemented, populated with local recruits and partners.  Where necessary, operational funds are sought through local investors.  The result being a cost-effective and market adaptive Japanese business structure that is tailored to the business parameters of the US corporation. Our role is to provide an enterpreneurship foundation during the startup mode, which can then maneuver its own growth path. With our experiences of 6 US startups and 4 turnarounds in the Japanese market, we believe we are the most qualified  to deliver this unique service. Source: [Imari Partners](http://www.imaripartners.com/)

Description: This business plan focuses on the key elements involved in the commercialization.
Headquarters Regions: Western US
Full Description: This business plan focuses on the key elements involved in the commercialization of a device built using entomology research conducted at Northern Arizona University. This research discovered that certain insect species, primarily wood boring beetles use sound to communicate. By creating acoustic profiles specific to a given species that alter and distort the normal sounds used by these insects to communicate it is possible to disrupt their behavior. This disruption can result in evacuation of a tree, halting of the mating process and even death of the target insects. The technology can be used to treat and prevent the infestation of wood boring insects in live growth trees, which is the basis of the product, herein referred to as Acoustic Disruption Technology (ADT).

Description: Online Reviews
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Squawkbox is a personalized guide created by you.   Right now, you have two choices when you want ratings and reviews online.  You can use a site that shows you everyone's opinions, but you have to go through a time consuming process to figure out who you can trust, who you should ignore, and so on.  Or, you can get a curated guide, where a company sends a reviewer every few years to write a review.  When reading, you don't know if the reviewer has anything in common with you, or if they get special treatment that you could never hope to get. Squawkbox combines the best of both of these, allowing anyone to give reviews, and allowing you to assemble your own team of reviewers you trust.  And if you want to share your opinions, you can use Squawkbox to broadcast your knowledge to the world and gain a following as the respected critic you've always wanted to be!
